{
  "stem": "1965.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 222.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But I think that each negativity that comes along the way, we should have the courage and the understanding to turn it into a positive.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Because we who continue must always continue for the better, and not for the worse.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, as you know, in most domestic worlds, there are peaceful worlds and not such peaceful worlds.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And unfortunately, in my family life, there was a lot of breakdowns of communications.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when you have breakdowns of communication, not understanding one with the other, there seems to be always an issue of heated elements-- which, as a child, leaves a certain-- you-- you become-- I-- I did-- I-- it did not affect me to become negative.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Contraire, it allowed me to go deeper within my own thoughts to analyze why two people cannot live in peace together.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as you know, I am now married-- in May, 34 years.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I will say, rating from a 1 to a 10, we have achieved a 9, which is pretty high today, isn't it, Sontha?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I learned to undo-- to do better-- from observing and experiencing firsthand.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What did you observe and experience-- at home?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think I would want to really go into details, because both my parents are not here.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're not alive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And may they rest in peace.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I love them, and I always will love them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I think that sometimes things happen in human being's life that they don't ask for.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It just happen because two elements did not really fit into the groove.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you know what goes on in-- nowadays in family life.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I feel bad for every woman, for every child, for every man that goes through the stresses of family life.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It needn't be.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
